{
  "texts": [
    "More commonly, however, the source and lens are reconstructed together.",
    "Consider an extended source with brightness distribution s(β).",
    "When lensed, this source will produce an extended image system",
    "where δ [...] is the delta function.",
    "The lens modeling problem is now to recover α(θ) and s(β) from observations of I (θ) and any other available information."
  ]
}